import { IHttpApiBridge, MediaType } from "../../../httpApiBridge";
 
export interface IAutoDeserializeConfirmService {
    /**
     * Send the response received for positive test cases here to verify that it has been serialized and deserialized properly.
     * 
     */
    confirm(endpoint: string, index: number, body: any): Promise<void>;
}
 
export class AutoDeserializeConfirmService {
    constructor(private bridge: IHttpApiBridge) {
    }
 
    public confirm(endpoint: string, index: number, body: any): Promise<void> {
        return this.bridge.callEndpoint<void>({
            data: body,
            endpointName: "confirm",
            endpointPath: "/confirm/{endpoint}/{index}",
            headers: {
            },
            method: "POST",
            pathArguments: [
                endpoint,
 
                index,
            ],
            queryArguments: {
            },
            requestMediaType: MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON,
            responseMediaType: MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON,
        });
    }
}
